style.css:
@-moz-document domain("roblox.com") {
.builder-font .text,
    .builder-font body,
    .builder-font button,
    .builder-font html,
    .builder-font input,
    .builder-font pre,
    .builder-font select,
    .builder-font textarea,
    .builder-font,
    .builder-font .h1,
    .builder-font .h2,
    .builder-font .h3,
    .builder-font .h4,
    .builder-font .h5,
    .builder-font .h6,
    .builder-font h1,
    .builder-font h2,
    .builder-font h3,
    .builder-font h4,
    .builder-font h5,
    .builder-font h6 {
        font-family: "HCo Gotham SSm", Gotham, Montserrat, "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "Lucida Grande", sans-serif;
    }
    
    .builder-font .game-card-container .game-card-name {
        font-weight: 500;
    }
}
